Six deaths reported across the UK today; 3 in England.

This is the lowest number since 2 March 2020 - i.e, since the #COVID19 pandemic began.

Come on, guys: it's over. Congratulations on the magnificent #vaccine roll-out. Now, let's get back to real normal life.
